description:
Pete is an artist who specializes in abstracts.
“I like to paint interesting perspectives,” he told me. “I like using unusual colors and textures too.”
He says he paints just enough to earn a living.
“I love going to the gym, the beach, the park... whatever,” he explained. “So I can paint when I want and do what I want.”
He’s got a lot of muscle already but he says he want to put on more.
“It’s never enough,” he said with a chuckle. “I want to put on another fifteen pounds or so. I’m working on it...”
Pete’s got a long, beautiful dick with a large head.
“Do you ever get compliments on your dick?” I asked.
He looked at the ground and smiled. “Yes,” he said. “I do...”
title: Pete
